TopicTitle: Well, Where did i go today?

Articles.Content:
Had an afternoon free, so wanted to put a probe on the Mun, and it went so well i decided to go for minmus too:

That was so successful, i thought i would go for Eve!:

Was really happy with the succes of the missions, next i plan to do a manned return mission to the moons of kerbin and one of the further planets. Well happy with my afternoons progress!
Nice, next afternoon you will be landing on the rest of the main planets.
